Bt:	Bit Test
Bts:	Bit Test and Set to one
Btr:	Bit Test and Reset to zero
Btc:	Bit Test and Compliment (toggle)

These bit test operations are "atomic" meaning they won't be interrupted 
between the testing of the bit and the alteration.  This is important when 
multitasking.  With multiprocessing, you should "Lock" these operations.

